wrap-regex.description:
Description

This is used to disambiguate the slash operator and facilitates more readable code.

Example ofincorrectcode for this rule:

/*eslint wrap-regex: "error"*/

function a() {
    return /foo/.test("bar");
}

Example ofcorrectcode for this rule:

/*eslint wrap-regex: "error"*/

function a() {
    return (/foo/).test("bar");
}
